{"tid":749762,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"已經證明咗關愛座hunter係屈毛","createTime":"2018-07-20T09:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T06:21:42.000Z","uid":99568,"like":21,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1771e4141b0ab6289025facf4888e50eac9bc3b4","tid":749762,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/173655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F173655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=52945e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲就係佢所謂嘅（五毛）證據<br />\n<br />\n你條垃圾淨係識得屈毛， 斷章取義我話梁天琦傻仔因為佢居然為咗香港放棄佢美好嘅前途， 佢係一個大 偉人 但係同時間亦都係一個 冇為自己打算嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/174013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F174013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=39c2b78f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔怪得知關sir成日用埋曬啲低莊手段原來係想上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe8af6d51a8bb4537bdf6464ce14e8bf3043b9a","tid":749762,"uid":99568,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"次次我駁佢又答唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44ad913cb47136949a28318aee064453f9458de","tid":749762,"uid":99568,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"淨係識入嚟貼我嘅起底資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪就係因為佢屈我唔到毛"},{"pid":"4cf0263cbf44c18d449bd2735bb117a35d06ade7","tid":749762,"uid":99568,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾開始追擊我係因為 立法會補選嗰陣 我串佢叫人唔好投票畀姚松炎， 跟住之後條垃圾就開始嬲嬲豬追擊我<br />\n<br />\n宜家姚松炎輸咗 工聯會條友當選咗關sir 係咪得償所願啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人形豬五毛關</span></span>"},{"pid":"575583ffefd6581b75e6a9fce3108bb6b100bb56","tid":749762,"uid":99568,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"關sir比起平時慢咗， 關sir其實你知唔知道如果你覆得唔夠快 工聯會唔會出糧畀你㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bba8fabf07fc0de5d6215ccff9d3954b27b053","tid":749762,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"歡迎關愛座入嚟接我畀人起底嘅資料， 因為咁樣 先證明咗 條撚樣 冇嘢入我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src